<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="disturb-vt">disturb <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'stɜːb/    美 /dɪ'stɜːrb/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>打扰；扰乱；使心神不安：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Sorry to disturb you</strong>, but can I talk to you for a minute? 
抱歉打扰您，我能跟您聊一会儿吗？</p></div></div>